properties.name: ApplicationId
properties.summary: Gets or sets the application associated with the current token.

properties.name: AuthorizationId
properties.summary: Gets or sets the authorization associated with the current token.

properties.name: CreationDate
properties.summary: Gets or sets the UTC creation date of the current token.

properties.name: ExpirationDate
properties.summary: Gets or sets the UTC expiration date of the current token.

properties.name: Payload
properties.summary:
Gets or sets the payload of the current token, if applicable.
            Note: this property is only used for reference tokens
            and may be encrypted for security reasons.

properties.name: Properties
properties.summary:
Gets or sets the additional properties serialized as a JSON object,
            or null if no bag was associated with the current token.

properties.name: RedemptionDate
properties.summary: Gets or sets the UTC redemption date of the current token.

properties.name: ReferenceId
properties.summary:
Gets or sets the reference identifier associated
            with the current token, if applicable.
            Note: this property is only used for reference tokens
            and may be hashed or encrypted for security reasons.

properties.name: Status
properties.summary: Gets or sets the status of the current token.

properties.name: Subject
properties.summary: Gets or sets the subject associated with the current token.

properties.name: Type
properties.summary: Gets or sets the type of the current token.

properties.name: Description
properties.summary: Gets or sets the public description associated with the current scope.

properties.name: Descriptions
properties.summary:
Gets or sets the localized public descriptions associated
            with the current scope, serialized as a JSON object.

properties.name: DisplayName
properties.summary: Gets or sets the display name associated with the current scope.

properties.name: DisplayNames
properties.summary:
Gets or sets the localized display names
            associated with the current application,
            serialized as a JSON object.

properties.name: Name
properties.summary: Gets or sets the unique name associated with the current scope.

properties.name: Properties
properties.summary:
Gets or sets the additional properties serialized as a JSON object,
            or null if no bag was associated with the current scope.

properties.name: Resources
properties.summary:
Gets or sets the resources associated with the
            current scope, serialized as a JSON array.
